，越看越闹心。", "content_rendered": "<p>国内网站，尤其是文字类型的网站，比如知乎微博，现在好好说话、有效输出的少，高强度地喷 /团建的很多。</p>\n<p>比如下面这个话题，一水地团建 /反团建，有价值的回答没几个。\n歼-20 已经入空军序列 6 周年，这 6 年来，你觉得最令你难忘的是什么？ - 知乎: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/588450473\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/588450473</a></p>\n<p>微博上呢，煽动男女对立情绪的非常多</p>\n<p>B 站稍微好点，毕竟知乎微博会打字就行，制作视频就很费劲，但 B 站的评论区 /弹幕的质量也开始有这种趋势。</p>\n<p>真的是看不下去了，越看越闹心。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1683437920, "replies": 36, "id": 938022}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 55628, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8370, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 429891, "username": "idragonet", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/idragonet", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3acd/5809/429891_mini.png?m=1652947337", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3acd/5809/429891_normal.png?m=1652947337", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3acd/5809/429891_large.png?m=1652947337", "created": 1563323820, "last_modified": 1652947337}, "last_reply_by": "EarthChild", "last_touched": 1683447267, "title": "“国产化” 大家选择什么数据库？人大金仓？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/937986", "created": 1683422091, "deleted": 0, "content": "有免费的“国产”数据库推荐吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>有免费的“国产”数据库推荐吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1683422091, "replies": 32, "id": 937986}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "htt